<SceneText>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>シング</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Shing</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>コハク</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kohaku</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>コハク……やっぱりついてくるの？
危ないし、コハクにまたなにかあったら……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kohaku... you're coming after all?
It's dangerous.
If something happened to you again...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>シング！　もう言わないの！
それに、シングが世界を滅ぼしかけたのは
わたしのせいでもあるんだから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Shing! No more of that!
Besides, it's my fault, too, that you
had almost destroyed the world.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>一人で全部引き受けようなんてズルいよ。
わたしだって頑張らなきゃ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's not fair for you to take responsibility
for that by yourself.
I have to do my best, too.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>わかった、一緒にガンドコいこう！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Got it. Let's go to Gandoku together!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うん！　</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
